'''kon-yo''' - this refers to those who belong in the upper class society and loves to show off. This word is used to define people who wants the world to know that they are not just an average-class individual. Persons referred to as ''konyo'', are those who most likely come out with flashy accessories and/or expensive clothings for others to notice. They would rather choose to be looked up to and be treated as '''''VIPs'''''.